{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05449/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05449"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:54:49"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["three shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman stand on either side of a doorway as another woman passes through."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05449","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05449"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1/77e507b1-532e-461d-a269-06f1ff4416a9","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:52:26.436Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>For the film’s press kit, PTA said, “Daniel is so handsome, but we made a film together [<em>There Will be Blood</em>] in which he was rather ugly in terms of character and setting . . . I started thinking how I could make him more handsome, seeing how fashionable he was in his everyday life, and knowing well his love for clothing and grooming and making things with his hands” (“About the Production,” 6-7).</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:578.4102637614703,65.18205275229384,522.65625,586.2170298165137"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1/efd14740-39d0-4d62-88dc-2bed6144a364","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:53:05.101Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When Reynolds cannot get his way with the older woman, he has Alma act for him. On the one hand, he does so to avoid the social impropriety of a man undressing a sleeping woman (Barbara Rose). On the other hand, he seems childlike in this scene, behaving like a young boy going to his mother for help. The scene emphasizes the maternal role Alma has taken in his life and the beginnings of his willingness to allow her to take control of him.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05449/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:18.619552752295903,37.73079128440404,305.34690366972484,255.77694954128444"}}}]}]}]}